  "remarks": "Russian foreign travel passport number 620169661. Russian national passport number 9103314932, issued on 15 Aug. 2003 (issued by Department of the Federal Migration Service of the Russian Federation for the Republic Karachayevo-Cherkessia). As at Aug. 2015, emir of Russian-speaking militants of the Islamic State of Iraq and the Levant (ISIL), listed as Al-Qaida in Iraq (QDe.115). Controls the Syrian Arab Republic cities of Al Dana and Idlib as an ISIL chief. Wanted by the authorities of the Russian Federation for terrorist crimes committed in its territory. Photo available for inclusion in the INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020.; Listing: Listed on 2 Oct. 2015 (amended on 24 Nov. 2020)",
